<![CDATA[<div><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi&nbsp;</font><font face="arial">{!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Would you like to be a part of a team of NCS graduates who form a hospitality team that supports an important event that increases awareness around social mixing? The event, which partly run by The Challenge, is aimed at politicians, policy makers, businesses and charities.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">This event will explore the opportunities people have to mix across lines of difference and consider the benefits of increased social contact between different groups of people.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">On the day you would;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">o Arrive at around 4.15pm&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">o Help with some of the set up of the room</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">o Welcome guests on arrival and check them off on the register</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">o Oversee the refreshments to ensure they stay well stocked</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">o Participate in the event</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Date: Thursday 20th November</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Location:&nbsp;</font><font color="#000000" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Fusion Centre, South and City College&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">B5 5SU</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">If you would like to support this high profile event and learn more about this important agenda then email&nbsp;</font><a href="mailto:afua.kudom@the-challenge.org" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family: Helvetica57-Condensed, sans-serif; line-height: 12.2666673660278px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">afua.kudom@the-challenge.org</a><font face="arial">&nbsp;by 9am Thursday 20th November.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div></div>]]></td>
